# Merge into ~/.openclaw/workspace/TOOLS.md (or create if missing)

### Site pulse

- **URL to check** (must match `.site-pulse-url`): `https://your-site.com/`
- **One-line config file:** `~/.openclaw/workspace/.site-pulse-url` (copy from `.site-pulse-url.example` in this repo)

Add any other notes for your environment (SSH hosts, API bases, etc.).
